Module com.example.sesion4
Package com.example.sesion4.model

Interface EnemigoInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
Enemigo
public interface EnemigoInterface
Interface that defines the contract for enemy behavior in the game. Provides methods for initializing enemy state, performing enemy actions, and accessing the enemy's game grid.

    • inicializar

      void inicializar()
      Initializes the enemy's state and prepares it for gameplay. This should be called before any other methods are used.
